``--keep-last``
 flag for 
``uniq-by``
 command (#17564)
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/17562] refactor: deprecated datasource-ls in favor of path-columns (#17562)
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/17560] feat(commands): added path_columns metadata for 
``du``
 command (#17560)
@fdncred:
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/17594] fixed 
``is-empty``
 / 
``is-not-empty``
 on 
``Empty``
 Pipelines (#17594)
